@startuml
title Alur RSS → AI Sentiment (Hybrid Model Buatan Sendiri)

start

:RSS News Data (Judul, Isi, Source);

:Preprocessing Text;
note right
- lowercase
- cleaning
- stopword removal
- stemming
end note

:Feature Engineering;
note right
- TF-IDF
- Word2Vec / FastText
- IndoBERT embedding
end note

fork

  :Model A - Lexicon Based;
  note right
  Kamus kata:
  positif / negatif scoring
  end note

fork again

  :Model B - ML Classifier;
  note right
  SVM / Naive Bayes / Logistic Regression
  end note

fork again

  :Model C - Deep Learning;
  note right
  LSTM / BiLSTM / IndoBERT fine-tuned
  end note

end fork

:Ensemble Engine;
note right
Gabungkan semua hasil model:
Weighted scoring / voting
end note

:Final Sentiment Output;
note right
Positive / Neutral / Negative
Confidence score
end note

:Save to Database;

:Dashboard Analytics;

stop

@enduml